main_body:
The following points (d) and (e) shall be added to the first subparagraph of Article 1 of Decision 2006/784/EC:
‘(d) the Autofom apparatus and the assessment methods related thereto, details of which are given in Part 4 of the Annex;
(e) the UltraFom 300 apparatus and the assessment methods related thereto, details of which are given in Part 5 of the Annex.’
